    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Those parts of complete rounds of ammunition, either cartridges or shells, that encase the charge, primer and, usually, the projectile.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
